oid(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107834)\">Matt. 5:17-18<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">10. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107945\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107945)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107945)\">Matt. 11:12-13<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113232\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113232)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113232)\">D&amp;C 13:1<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114670\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114670)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114670)\">D&amp;C 84:27<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108297\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108297)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108297)\">Mark 1:2-3<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109837\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109837)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109837)\">Eph. 5:23<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109895\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109895)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109895)\">Col. 1:18<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109791\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109791)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109791)\">Eph. 2:20<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110425\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110425)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110425)\">1 Pet. 2:6<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109498\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(